Application of graph 
1.Google maps uses graphs for building transportation systems. Where intersection of two(or more) roads are considered to be a vertex and the road connecting two
2.It is used to represent connection between individuals  on social media platforms
3.On social media sites, graphs are used to track the data of the users. liked showing preferred post suggestions, recommendations.
4.It used to not only show directions on maps but to also calculate the shortest route.
5. Used on social media platform to detect a community i.e people sharing similar demographic characteristics. This helps with social media marketing by targeting certain group and not everyone.
6.Search Engines: Graphs are used to analyze and rank web pages for search engine results, using algorithms like PageRank.
